There's a new way to get around the new update:

1. press guide button ...sign in to modded profile ...as soon as the profile picture stats to show up press guide button again to sign in successfully..

2. start the game.. it will tell u to sign it with the profile that has bought the game...

3. IMPORTANT********

select sign in..

but don't select profile..

instead press Y to create new profile.

4. now press guide button again. the pop up window be gone..

5. now press guide button again and sign out of modded profile and sign in to ur own profile....
